---
<section id="install" class="px-6 py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <div class="mb-3 text-center text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-accent">Install</div>
    <h2 class="text-center font-heading text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight md:text-4xl">Install via Helm.</h2>
    <p class="mx-auto mb-14 mt-3 max-w-[60ch] text-center text-base text-ink-muted md:text-lg">
      Two charts: CRDs first, then the operator. Pulls from GHCR's OCI registry.
    </p>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[720px] overflow-x-auto rounded-lg bg-code-bg px-8 py-7 font-mono text-sm leading-7 text-code-ink shadow-lg">
<pre class="m-0"><code class="bg-transparent p-0 font-mono text-inherit">
<span class="text-code-stone">$</span> <span>helm upgrade --install frp-operator-crd \</span>
      <span class="text-code-lime">oci://ghcr.io/mtaku3/charts/frp-operator-crd</span> \
      <span class="text-code-amber">--version</span> <span class="text-code-lime">0.0.1</span> \
      <span class="text-code-amber">--namespace</span> <span class="text-code-lime">frp-operator-system</span> <span class="text-code-amber">--create-namespace</span>

<span class="text-code-stone">$</span> <span>helm upgrade --install frp-operator \</span>
      <span class="text-code-lime">oci://ghcr.io/mtaku3/charts/frp-operator</span> \
      <span class="text-code-amber">--version</span> <span class="text-code-lime">0.0.1</span> \
      <span class="text-code-amber">--namespace</span> <span class="text-code-lime">frp-operator-system</span>

<span class="italic text-code-stone"># Operator running. Apply your first ExitPool next.</span>
</code></pre>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
